  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA21">
<l>avaṉē yirucuṭartī yākāca māvā</l>
<l>ṉavaṉē puvipuṉalkāṟ ṟāvā - ṉavaṉē</l>
<l>yiyamāṉaṉā yaṭṭa mūrttiyumāy ñāṉa</l>
<l>mayaṉāki niṉṟāṉum vantu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He, he is the two lights, fire, ether.</l>
<l>He, he is the earth, the flood, the wind. He, he is also</l>
<l>the one who comes [and] stands as sacrificer and as eight forms,</l>
<l>being one who consists of knowledge.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
